# AuroraStyleSheet
tags: $StyleSheet
```css
:root {
  --colbg1: #0e1626;
  --colbg2: #18233a;
  --colbg3: #1f2d49;
  --colbgi: #0b1220;
  --colfg:  #dce6f5;
  --colfgi: #eaf2ff;
  --col0:   #02060d;
  --col1:   #6f8bb5;
  --col3:   #2a9d8f;
  --col4:   #33507f;
  --col6:   #5fe1c6;
  --notify-rgba: 47, 157, 143;
  --rad1: 14px;
  --rad2: 14px;
  --rad3: 14px;
  --rad4: 14px;
}

* {
  font-family: "Segoe UI", system-ui, sans-serif;
}

body {
  background:
    radial-gradient(900px 500px at 100% -10%, rgba(95, 225, 198, 0.10), transparent 60%),
    radial-gradient(700px 500px at -10% 0%, rgba(51, 80, 127, 0.35), transparent 55%),
    var(--colbg1);
}

div#header {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1f2d49, #142038);
  border: 1px solid #33507f;
  box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
}

div#sidebar {
  background: rgba(31, 45, 73, 0.6);
  border: 1px solid #2c4474;
}

div.tiddler {
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1a2740, #162033);
  outline: none;
  border: 1px solid #2c4474;
  box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
}

div.tiddler div.title {
  background: transparent;
  color: #bfe9df;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}

a:not([class]) {
  color: #5fe1c6;
}

button {
  background: #21507a;
  color: #dce6f5;
}

code {
  color: #9af0dc;
}
```

A light editorial theme with serif headlines and a centered reading column.

